  "active_lock_reason": null,
  "body": "To prevent transaction spamming, most clients are implementing a FIFO ordering among transactions with the same gas price. From the code below, it looks like we already do that. However, it seems like we don't order by gas price, which is a problem for maximizing mining profits.\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/hyperledger/besu/blob/7b9ade23cde145e67f90112d3411e80f860129f6/ethereum/eth/src/main/java/org/hyperledger/besu/ethereum/eth/transactions/PendingTransactions.java#L72-L76\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\nEnsure that we order by gas price and then by time. If we don't do either, implement and test.\r\n",
